4. CONTAINER WITH MOST WATER
   Problem: Find max area between two lines
   Approach:
       left = 0, right = n-1
       maxArea = 0
       while left < right:
           height = min(arr[left], arr[right])
           width = right - left
           area = height * width
           maxArea = max(maxArea, area)
           if arr[left] < arr[right]:
               left++
           else:
               right--
       return maxArea

5. 3SUM
   Problem: Find all triplets that sum to zero
   Approach:
       sort array
       for i = 0 to n-3:
           left = i+1, right = n-1
           while left < right:
               sum = arr[i] + arr[left] + arr[right]
               if sum == 0:
                   add triplet to result
                   left++, right--
               elif sum < 0:
                   left++
               else:
                   right--

6. REMOVE DUPLICATES FROM SORTED ARRAY
   Problem: Remove duplicates in-place, return new length
   Approach:
       left = 0 (write pointer)
       right = 1 (read pointer)
       while right < n:
           if arr[left] != arr[right]:
               left++
               arr[left] = arr[right]
           right++
       return left + 1

